    public abstract class AbstractContainerDeserializer<T>
extends AbstractItem<T>
implements javax.json.bind.serializer.JsonbDeserializer<T>
    Base class for all deserializers producing non single value result. Deserialize bean objects, collections, maps, arrays, etc.
